borrowDebt(uint256,uint256,uint128).details: Calculates shares, checks liquidity, and handles cross-chain or local transfers. Accrues interest before borrowing.

params._amount: The amount of tokens to borrow.
params._chainId: The chain id of the destination network.

params._router: Address of the lending pool router

liquidation(address).details: Transfers borrow token from liquidator, sends collateral bonus to liquidator

params._borrower: The address of the borrower to liquidate

repayWithSelectedToken(address,address,u.custom:throws: ZeroAmount if _shares is 0.amountSharesInvalid if shares exceed user's borrow shares.
repayWithSelectedToken(address,address,u.details: Swaps selected token to borrow token if needed via position contract. Accrues interest before repayment.

params._amountOutMinimum: The slippage tolerance in basis points (e.g., 500 = 5%).
params._fromPosition: Whether to use tokens from the position contract (true) or from the user's wallet (false).
params._shares: The number of borrow shares to repay.
params._token: The address of the token to use for repayment.
params._user: The address of the user to repay the debt.

supplyCollateral(address,uint256).details: Transfers collateral tokens from user to their Position contract. Accrues interest before deposit.

params._amount: The amount of collateral tokens to supply.
params._user: The address of the user to supply collateral.

supplyLiquidity(address,uint256).details: Users receive shares proportional to their deposit. Shares represent ownership in the pool. Accrues interest before deposit.

params._amount: The amount of borrow tokens to supply as liquidity.
params._user: The address of the user to supply liquidity.

swapTokenByPosition(address,address,uint.details: Validates oracles for both tokens, checks health after swap

params._amountIn: Amount of input tokens to swap

withdrawCollateral(uint256).custom:throws: ZeroAmount if amount is 0.InsufficientCollateral if user has insufficient collateral balance.
withdrawCollateral(uint256).details: Transfers collateral tokens from Position contract back to user. Accrues interest before withdrawal.

params._amount: The amount of collateral tokens to withdraw.

withdrawLiquidity(uint256).details: Calculates the corresponding asset amount based on the proportion of total shares. Accrues interest before withdrawal.

params._shares: The number of supply shares to redeem for underlying tokens.

borrowDebt(uint256,uint256,uint128).notice: Borrow assets using supplied collateral and optionally send them to a different network.

repayWithSelectedToken(address,address,u.notice: Repay borrowed assets using a selected token from the user's position.

router().notice: Address of the lending pool router contract

supplyCollateral(address,uint256).notice: Supply collateral tokens to the user's position in the lending pool.

supplyLiquidity(address,uint256).notice: Supply liquidity to the lending pool by depositing borrow tokens.

withdrawCollateral(uint256).notice: Withdraw supplied collateral from the user's position.

withdrawLiquidity(uint256).notice: Withdraw supplied liquidity by redeeming shares for underlying tokens.
